.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c4002%2c20221130%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,111,聲,4002,20221130,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"4002","JDATE":"20221130","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}